title: About
text:
Hi, I’m Sarah, a Physician Assistant originally from Buffalo, NY, now living in the Stafford, VA area! I hold an undergraduate degree in Business Administration from the University at Buffalo and a PA degree from Daemen University d
My medical background includes 8 years in primary care, serving as a traveling PA providing customized care to my patients, and working as an Emergency Medicine PA. My newest passion as a PA brings me to the medical aesthetic industry, where I created Jazz Medical Aesthetics. Jazz Medical Aesthetics is a concierge medical aesthetic service customized to meet each patient’s aesthetic goal
